<taxonomicName id="4C064D718E4DFFDAFB04F854FAFD85FE" box="[1242,1310,1939,1963]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Athlia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="281" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B972EAE08E4DFFDAFB04F854FAFD85FE" box="[1242,1310,1939,1963]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="281">Athlia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The name is feminine in gender to match 
<taxonomicName id="4C064D718E4DFFDAFE2DF873FDD48599" box="[499,567,1972,1996]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Athlia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="281" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B972EAE08E4DFFDAFE2DF873FDD48599" box="[499,567,1972,1996]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="281">Athlia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
